lead_paragraph: Tommy Wingels made up for an early defensive mistake by scoring the game-winning goal to lift the San Jose Sharks over the Florida Panthers 4-2 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Wingels Scores Winner to Lead Sharks Over Panthers 4-2
